features: 🍀 REAL OR FAKE PLANT DECOR? - If you're not a fan of manual labor, our small fake plants for home decor are a fantastic way to add more attraction to your home without all the effort and hassle of taking care of live house plants. Enjoy the natural beauty of the plants without dirtying your hands!

🌵 DIMENSIONS - The 2 mini artificial succulents plants measure appr. 7cm tall and 7cm wide. The fake potted rosemary and eucalyptus are appr. 25cm tall (from top of the plant to the bottom of the pot) and 20cm wide (from tip to tip of the leaves). Arrange them together or let each one shine on its own in separate space!

🌿 HIGH QUALITY MATERIAL - Each faux plant is made of plastic and set in a sturdy paper pulp pot that has simulated foam soil. They require no trimming or watering and will stay fresh-looking all year long. Since these plant pots are made of paper pulp, please do not put them in water

🌵 LIGHTWEIGHT & WIDE APPLICATION - Small & Lightweight fake plants decor for easy styling. Perfect to display on your bookshelf, living room mantle, coffee table, dining room table, cabinet, counter space, desk, kitchen, window ledge, foyer and any other place to bring more lifelike colors and organic style. They also make a great gift for housewarming parties, weddings and holidays

🍀 100% SATISFACTION CUSTOMER SERVICE - Due to the uncertainty during shipping, the plant pots are probable to be broken. If you receive cracked products or you are not 100% satisfied with our artificial potted plants, please contact us immediately for a full refund or replacement risk-free
